00:17:44,541 --> 00:17:46,666
[VIDEL screams]

358
00:17:46,750 --> 00:17:48,125
[GOHAN grunts]

359
00:17:49,791 --> 00:17:51,166
[VIDEL] Huh?!

360
00:17:54,166 --> 00:17:57,458
[GOHAN] Excuse me, miss!
